'''杨梅黄酮'''（'''Myricetin'''）是一种天然的[[黄酮醇|黄酮醇]]，是存在于许多水果、蔬菜、浆果及药材等植物中的[[黄酮类化合物|黄酮类化合物]]。杨梅黄酮是红葡萄酒中的[[酚类化合物|酚类化合物]]之一。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://jme.endocrinology-journals.org/cgi/content/abstract/35/2/269 |title=The red wine phenolics piceatannol and myricetin act as agonists for estrogen receptor  in human breast cancer cells. M Maggiolini, A G Recchia, D Bonofiglio, S Catalano, A Vivacqua, A Carpino, V Rago, R Rossi and S Andò, Journal of Molecular Endocrinology (2005) 35 269-281 |access-date=2011-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100706174934/http://jme.endocrinology-journals.org/cgi/content/abstract/35/2/269 |archive-date=2010-07-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

杨梅黄酮可抗氧化。体外研究表明，高浓度的杨梅黄酮可降低[[低密度脂蛋白胆固醇|低密度脂蛋白胆固醇]]。芬兰的一项研究发现，高杨梅黄酮摄入的人群其[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]的发生率较低。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Knekt P, Kumpulainen J, Järvinen R, ''et al.'' |title=Flavonoid intake and risk of chronic diseases |journal=Am. J. Clin. Nutr. |volume=76 |issue=3 |pages=560–8 |pmid=12198000 |url=http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=12198000|date=September 2002}}</ref>

一项历时8年的研究发现，[[山柰酚|山柰酚]]、[[槲皮素|槲皮素]]和杨梅黄酮可降低吸烟者患胰腺癌的风险。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Nöthlings U, Murphy SP, Wilkens LR, Henderson BE, Kolonel LN |title=Flavonols and pancreatic cancer risk: the multiethnic cohort study |journal=Am. J. Epidemiol. |volume=166 |issue=8 |pages=924–31 |pmid=17690219 |doi=10.1093/aje/kwm172 |url=http://aje.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=17690219|date=October 2007}}</ref>

